# LEC Match Predictor

A machine learning project focused on predicting the outcomes of LEC (League of Legends EMEA Championship) matches.

## Current Status

<OLD> The project is currently in the data collection phase. I am gathering match data and using this opportunity to learn and practice web scraping, data preprocessing, and feature engineering techniques.

<CURRENT> Used data from Oracle's Elixir and Leaguepedia to create a baseline dataset, I need to feature engineer a lot more but I'm currently happy with the progress
## Goals

- Collect and organize LEC match data
- Build a dataset for training
- Train and evaluate prediction models
- Explore esports analytics and machine learning

🚧 Work in progress.
